              ZURK IV: "Enter the Ninja"                                        This sequel to ZURK III (what else?) details how the great adventurer increased his battle skills in an incredible tale in which he fought his way through an   ancient jungle temple and found a Magic Submarine. In the sub he traveled far   END                                                                             below the sea to an underground tavern. Arriving there he finds a strange       craft in which he can fly, and goes to battle with another craft which          mysteriously appears on the horizon. But the battle is fake. When they          END                                                                             land, he finds himself facing what appears to be the princess of ZURK III, who  calls herself Princess Milua Taj of Aldoron. She smiles and informs him that    the entire adventure was an amusement park!                                     FINISH                                                                          